    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are scoped out as acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application context. The assessment team notes that the model has been applied in clinical research investigations and the evidence base is sufficient to support an Accepted decision.",
